e</h1></header><nav><a href='#'>Home</a><a href='#'>About</a><a href='#'>Pricing</a></nav><main><section><h1>Pricing Plans</h1><div class='pricing-plans'><div class='plan'><h2>Basic</h2><p>$9.99/month</p><ul><li>Personalized workout planning</li><li>Nutrition tracking</li></ul><button>Sign Up</button></div><div class='plan'><h2>Premium</h2><p>$19.99/month</p><ul><li>Personalized workout planning</li><li>Nutrition tracking</li><li>Progress monitoring and analytics</li><li>Adaptive programming</li></ul><button>Sign Up</button></div></div></section></main><footer><p>&copy; 2024 FitForge</p><p><a href='#'>Terms of Service</a> | <a href='#'>Privacy Policy</a></p></footer></body></html>"
